<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NodCord - API Routes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            position: relative;
        }
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 40px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #575757;
        }
        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .section h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .routes-list {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .routes-list li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .routes-list a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .routes-list a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/assets/img/logo.png" alt="NodCord Logo">
            <span>NodCord</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/discord-members">Discord Members</a>
            <a href="/discord-servers">Discord Servers</a>
            <a href="/status">API Status</a>
            <a href="/info">Info</a>
            <a href="/docs">Documentation</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="section">
            <h1>API Routes</h1>
            <p>Below is a list of all available API routes:</p>
            <ul class="routes-list">
                <li><a href="/status">GET /status</a> - Returns the status of the application.</li>
                <li><a href="/discord/status">GET /discord/status</a> - Returns the status of the Discord bot.</li>
                <li><a href="/discord/restart">POST /discord/restart</a> - Restarts the Discord bot.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/products">GET /api/products</a> - List all products.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/products/:id">GET /api/products/:id</a> - Get a specific product by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/companies">GET /api/companies</a> - List all companies.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/companies/:id">GET /api/companies/:id</a> - Get a specific company by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/games">GET /api/games</a> - List all games.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/games/:id">GET /api/games/:id</a> - Get a specific game by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/projects">GET /api/projects</a> - List all projects.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/projects/:id">GET /api/projects/:id</a> - Get a specific project by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/tasks">GET /api/tasks</a> - List all tasks.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/tasks/:id">GET /api/tasks/:id</a> - Get a specific task by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/payments">GET /api/payments</a> - List all payments.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/payments/:id">GET /api/payments/:id</a> - Get a specific payment by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/groups">GET /api/groups</a> - List all groups.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/groups/:id">GET /api/groups/:id</a> - Get a specific group by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/chats">GET /api/chats</a> - List all chats.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/chats/:id">GET /api/chats/:id</a> - Get a specific chat by ID.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/favorites">GET /api/favorites</a> - List all favorites.</li>
                <li><a href="/api/favorites/:id">GET /api/favorites/:id</a> - Get a specific favorite by ID.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 NodCord. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>